Package dxf2svg.svg

Class Summary
DxfImageObjectReference This class Hold URI information about images that may be imbedded in the DXF file.
Point The Point class encapsulates the smallest element used in the conversion between DXF and SVG.
SvgArc This class encapsulates the SVG arc element.
SvgAttdef This immutable class encapsulates a DXF attribute definition, known as an ATTDEF, into an SVG format.
SvgAttrib This class encapsulates and converts the DXF object ATTRIB.
SvgCircle This class encapsulates the SVG circle element.
SvgCollection This class is the base class for all collections of SvgObjects.
SvgDimension This class encapsulates Dxf Dimension.
SvgDoubleEndedElementAggregate This class takes SvgDoubleEndedElements and combines their pathing attributes into one continuous path description.
SvgDoubleEndedGraphicElement This abstract class is the super class for all elements that have a start and end point.
SvgDxfHyperlink This object is analogous to HTML's 'a' element.
SvgElement SvgElement is the abstract base class for all Svg Objects.
SvgEllipse This class encapsulates the SVG ellipse element.
SvgEntityDeclaration This class encapsulates a collection of SvgObjects that, in the case of converting Dxf files, represents a block.
SvgEntityReference This class encapsulates Dxf INSERT object.
SvgFontMetrics This class represents the encapsulation of the metrics of a text styles font and line metrics.
SvgGraphicElement A graphic element object is defined here to be an empty class that needs to be sub-classed to be made into a useful SvgOject like SvgArc or Svgline or what ever.
SvgGroup This class encapsulates a generic grouping of SvgObjects.
SvgHatch SvgHatch encapsulates the Dxf object, HATCH.
SvgHatchLine This class encapsulates a line element that is used expressly for hatch patterns.
SvgHatchPattern This class encapsulates a hatch pattern.
SvgImage This class encapsulates images that is imbedded in a DXF.
SvgLayerGroup This class encapusulates all the SvgObjects that share a commonality of having come from the same layer in a DXF.
SvgLayerSubGroup Deprecated. March 05, 2004 This class is now exactly the same as a SvgLayerGroup but without any layer colour or layer name information.
SvgLine This class encapsulates the SVG line element.
SvgMPath An mpath is an object is a wrapper for a path reference that SvgAnimator uses to apply an animation effect along.
SvgMultiLineText This class encapsulate a Svg multi-line text object.
SvgNotes This class will generate the notes for a discreet series of illustration sheets.
SvgObject This class encapsulates the basic SVG object.
SvgObjectX This object could be any SvgObject you wish.
SvgPoint This class encapsulates the SVG point element.
SvgPolyLine This class encapsulates the SVG polyline element.
SvgReference This abstract class encapsulates an SvgReference of which there can be three types: SvgEntityReference, SvgUseXLink and SvgImage.
SvgSolid Encapsulates the Dxf object SOLID.
SvgSpline This class encapsulates curves whose Dxf equivilant is the spline object.
SvgSymbol Deprecated. This class and SvgUseXLink can be implemented if required but their original purpose has been superceded by SvgEntityReference and SvgEntityDeclaration
SvgText This class encapsulates a single line of text in SVG.
SvgUseXLink Deprecated. This class and SvgSymbol can be implemented if required but their original purpose has been superceded by SvgEntityReference and SvgEntityDeclaration
 

Exception Summary
NullSvgPointException This unchecked exception signals that the client application attempted to copy a Point object into a null reference.
NullUrlSvgReferenceException Gets thrown if an SvgReference object gets passed an empty or null URL.
